    "body" : "<p>You have to use the new <code>@ExtendWith</code> annotation.</p>\n<p>Unfortunately there is no extension released yet.\nOn <a href=\"https://github.com/junit-team/junit5-samples/blob/master/junit5-mockito-extension/src/main/java/com/example/mockito/MockitoExtension.java\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">github</a> you can see a beta implementation for the extension. as a example <a href=\"https://github.com/junit-team/junit5-samples/blob/master/junit5-mockito-extension/src/test/java/com/example/mockito/MockitoExtensionInBaseClassTest.java\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">demo test</a>.</p>\n"
