  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40961057/how-to-use-mockito-with-junit-5",
  "title" : "How to use Mockito with JUnit 5?",
  "body" : "<p>How can I use injection with Mockito and JUnit 5?</p>\n<p>In JUnit 4, I can just use the <code>@RunWith(MockitoJUnitRunner.class)</code> annotation.<br />\nIn JUnit 5, there is no <code>@RunWith</code> Annotation.</p>\n"
